name: Promo Code Pal
tag_list: coupon-codes, promo-codes, online-discounts, coupons, saving-money, online-shopping
overview:
Promo Code Pal is a leading online provider of online coupon codes, promo codes, voucher codes, and discounts to top online retailers.

We work directly with retailers to offer consumers the best online discounts. Our team spends countless hours each day looking for the best available deals so consumers save money and save time. We add new coupons every day and nearly every hour of the day.

Visitors to promocodepal.com can view and use coupons without registering. Visitors who do register can interact with other users on the site by commenting on coupons. Visitors can also stay on top of all the coupons we add by subscribing to our daily email.
